    ],
    "text": "Suspect Arrested in Connection with Money Laundering \u2013 Computer Crime Investigation Division, North Western Province Sub-Unit",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      247.0,
      523.62,
      315.48
    ],
    "text": "The North Western Province Sub-Unit of the Computer Crime Investigation Division initiated an investigation following a complaint alleging that a sum of Rs. 426,300/= (Four Hundred and Twenty-Six Thousand Three Hundred Rupees) had been fraudulently obtained by promising financial gains through an online business venture operated under a reputed brand name.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      329.92,
      524.5,
      398.4
    ],
    "text": "As a result of the investigation, a suspect was apprehended on 08.06.2026 in connection with the alleged money-laundering operation. Investigations have revealed that an amount of Rs. 186,500/= (One Hundred and Eighty-Six Thousand Five Hundred Rupees) from the defrauded funds had been transferred to the suspect\u2019s bank account.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      412.98,
      508.78,
      426.26
    ],
    "text": "The suspect is a 28-year-old woman residing in the Udugampola area of Gampaha.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      440.82,
      492.08,
      467.9
    ],
    "text": "Further inquiries are being conducted by officers attached to the North Western Province Sub-Unit of the Computer Crime Investigation Division.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      514.05,
      526.95,
      558.34
    ],
    "text": "02. \u0db3\u0ddc\u0db1 \u0dc4\u0dbd\u0dca\u0db4\u0dda \u0daf\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba \u0dc4\u0dbb\u0dc3\u0dca \u0db8\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0dca\u0d9c\u0db4\u0dda \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd4 \u0dc0\u0dd6 \u0daf\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba \u0d85\u0db1\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0db4\u0daf\u0db4\u0daf\u0db4\u0db1\u0d9a\u0dd4 \u0da2\u0dd3\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dad\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dba\u0da7 - \u0db3\u0ddc\u0db1 \u0db4 \u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca \u0dd9\u0dc3\u0db8.",
