    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      545.56,
      510.85,
      579.73
    ],
    "text": "Two Persons Killed in Train Collision at Halpe Railway Crossing \u2013 Kandana Police Division",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      596.61,
      522.39,
      637.49
    ],
    "text": "A tragic railway accident occurred on the morning of 09.06.2026 at the Halpe railway crossing within the Kandana Police Division when a train travelling from Chilaw to Colombo Fort collided with a three-wheeler attempting to cross the railway track.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      651.93,
      497.08,
      679.01
    ],
    "text": "The driver of the three-wheeler and a female passenger travelling in the rear seat sustained fatal injuries and died as a result of the collision.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      693.57,
      480.1,
      706.85
    ],
    "text": "The deceased, aged 48 and 71 respectively, were residents of the Ja-Ela area.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      721.41,
      523.22,
      762.19
    ],
    "text": "Preliminary investigations have disclosed that the three-wheeler had proceeded across the railway crossing despite the warning bell and signal lights being activated to indicate the approaching train.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      31.91,
      477.78,
      58.99
    ],
    "text": "The bodies are due to be forwarded to the Ragama Hospital for post-mortem examinations.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      73.57,
      512.74,
      86.85
    ],
    "text": "Further investigations into the incident are being carried out by the Kandana Police.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
